{"TopicId":182767,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"I have a challenge for everyone.","CreatedByName":"B00st3r","CreatedById":195323,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T08:22:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"B00st3r","CreatedById":195323,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T08:22:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:26px;\u0022\u003ETHE \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E CHALLENGE:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe human\u0027s have polluted earth, The sun is very big now, what can we do? I have the answer: Go to space. A lot of companies down at earth are competing to find the best solution.\u003Cbr\u003E\n-\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003ESpacex\u0027s solution:\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003EBuild an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to mars\u003Cbr\u003E\n-\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EULA\u0027s solution:\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003EBuild an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly to the moon, maybe its cold and dark, but its close \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n-\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EBlue origin\u0027s solution:\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003EBuild a single stage orbital colony, and let earth restore itself whilst we live in space\u003Cbr\u003E\n-\u003Cb\u003E\u003Ci\u003ENASA\u0027s solution:\u00A0\u003C/i\u003E\u003C/b\u003EBuild an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E to pluto, it will never get eaten by the sun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou choose which solution you believe in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EPhase 1: Rookie division \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E builder\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Build a functional \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EPhase 2: Neil armstrong Jr.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n-Build an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u00A0in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to the moon and back (Mission must be manned)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EPhase 3: Elon musk\u0027s little helper\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n-Build a manned\u00A0\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to at least 5\u00A0biomes on mars\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cb\u003EPhase 4: Humanity\u0027s savior\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nBuild a manned \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to Pluto and all its moons then back to earth.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cu\u003ENOTE: i am not a mod on the KSP forums so i cant put any titles to your name\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-03-10T10:25:59Z\u0022 title=\u002203/10/2019 10:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 10, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by B00st3r\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T08:41:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst off, it belongs to challenges subforum, second, are\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eyou\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003Eable to build a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to Pluto and back?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"B00st3r","CreatedById":195323,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T08:56:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223555509\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552207286\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsecond, are\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eyou\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003Eable to build a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E and fly it to Pluto and back?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNearly, got a few calculations wrong when it came to delta vee, but i was able to complete face 1, 2 and 3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atkara","CreatedById":169458,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T09:45:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223555511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552208170\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022195323\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022B00st3r\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, B00st3r said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNearly, got a few calculations wrong when it came to \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, but i was able to complete \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ephase\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A01, 2 and 3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever played around with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E myself. The backstory maybe pointing out at a mass exodus, which shouldn\u0027t be done with SSTOs (in other words, craft hauling sections they could\u0027ve filled with people, instead of fuel)\u00A0but I understand people may find this challenge interesting \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aeroboi","CreatedById":186653,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T10:26:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003Erss\u003C/abbr\u003E variant challenge using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s is a little to big of a leap unless you use exotic/future engine mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe on a 3x kerbin scale the challenge is more universal and more people will apply. Still, it\u0027s good to see a rather alternative challenge posted \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-10T13:10:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis challenge has been moved to the Challenges section of the forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP Moderation Team\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"joshudson","CreatedById":123912,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-12T02:06:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere\u0027s the Orion Drive when you need it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow","CreatedById":65767,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T23:57:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Ooh\u0022 I thought, \u0022a challenge for everyone.\u0022\u00A0 Except that it isn\u0027t.\u00A0 It\u0027s only a challenge for anyone who is running the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E mod.\u00A0 Bummer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}